==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Townsman
<hw>Towns"man</hw> <pr>(tounz"m⟦ait⟧n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Townsmen</plw>
<pr>(tounz"m⟦eit⟧n)</pr>.</plu>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>An inhabitant of a town; one of the same town with
another.</def> <rj><au>Pope.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A selectman, in New England. See
<er>Selectman</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Townspeople</ent>⟦br⟧
